fields.name: Matte Lipsticks Box | Set of 3
fields.description: A set of 3 long-lasting matte lipsticks in a variety of bold, rich shades, perfect for all-day wear.

fields.name: Matte Lip Crayon | Won't Smudge Won't Budge
fields.description: A highly pigmented matte lip crayon that glides on smoothly and stays in place all day without smudging.

fields.name: Super Stay | Non Transfer Lipstick
fields.description: A non-transferable matte lipstick that stays intact for hours, giving you a bold, vibrant color without fading.

fields.name: Color Balm Lipstick
fields.description: A moisturizing lip balm with a tint of color that nourishes and hydrates your lips while providing a soft, natural finish.

fields.name: Creamy Matte Lipstick
fields.description: A creamy matte lipstick that offers intense color payoff with a comfortable, lightweight feel.

fields.name: Matte Lipstick | Non Transfer Butter Stick
fields.description: A buttery smooth, non-transferable matte lipstick that delivers bold color with a soft, velvety finish.

fields.name: Matte Lip Color
fields.description: A richly pigmented matte lip color that offers long-lasting wear with a smooth, comfortable texture.

fields.name: Candylicious | Lip Gloss
fields.description: A high-shine lip gloss with a candy-sweet scent, giving your lips a glossy, luscious finish.
